@model KyoS.Web.Models.IntakeNoDuplicateServiceViewModel
<div class="col-md-12">
    <pre>
    Client Name: <strong>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Name) </strong> 
         Record: <strong>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Code)</strong> 
    </pre>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
    <pre>
    <strong>NO DUPLICATE SERVICE ACKNOWLEDGEMENT</strong>

    I hereby acknowledge that, at the time of signing this form, I am assuredly not receiving Community Mental and Behavioral Health services through any other agency or provider 
    and that I am requesting this type of services only from <u><strong>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Clinic.Name)</strong></u> 
    I certify that the above statement is true and correct to the best of my knowledge. I understand that duplication of services may constitutes fraud under federal and state laws
    related to Medicaid and Medicare and that a false statement may disqualify me for services and affect my benefits.
    __________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

    Yo, reconozco que, al momento de firmar este formulario, no estoy recibiendo servicios en la Comunidad de Salud Mental y del Comportamiento a través de otra agencia o proveedor 
    y que estoy solicitando este tipo de servicios solamente en <u><strong>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Clinic.Name)</strong></u> 
    Certifico que la declaración anterior es verdadera y correcta en lo mejor de mi conocimiento. Entiendo que la duplicación de servicios puede constituir un fraude bajo 
    las leyes federales y estatales relacionadas con Medicaid y Medicare que una declaración falsa puede descalificarme para los servicios y afectar mis beneficios.
    </pre>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
    <pre>
    
    <strong>Person served signature date</strong>    <input asp-for="DateSignaturePerson">      <strong>Legal Guardian signature date</strong>    <input asp-for="DateSignatureLegalGuardian">
    <strong>(@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Name))</strong>     
    
    <strong>Employee signature date</strong>         <input asp-for="DateSignatureEmployee">
    <strong>(@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.AdmissionedFor))</strong>                                                                    
    </pre>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
    &nbsp;
</div>
<div>
    <div class="form-group col-md-12">
        <input type="checkbox" asp-for="Documents" class="form-check-input" id="Documents"> Documents were verbally translated to me in my native language.<br />
        <label asp-for="Documents" class="forgot">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => Model.Client.Clinic.Name)</strong>
        </label>
    </div>
</div>
